The paper presents a mapping robot with support for external tracking system and uses a 3D scanner for ground truth map collection. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of mapping algorithms using generated datasets, which could fall under Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
